Maven SVN Revision Number Plugin

    This plugin retrieves the revision number and the status of the Subversion working copy directory.

    The {{{http://svnkit.com/}SVNKit}} library is used for all Subversion-related operations.

* Goals Overview

    * {{{./revision-mojo.html}${project.artifactId}:release}} Retrieves the status and revision number of a file or a
        directory under Subversion version control.

* Using the plugin

    General instructions on how to use the ${project.name} can be found on the {{{./usage.html}usage page}}. Some more
    specific use cases are described in the examples given below.

    If you feel like the plugin is missing a feature or has a defect, you can fill a feature request or bug report in our
    {{{./issue-tracking.html}issue tracker}}. When creating a new issue, please provide a comprehensive description of your
    concern.

